                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div id="best-deal">
    <div class="container" style="background: white; padding: 35px 25px;">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 text-left fh5co-heading animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                <h2>要闻快讯</h2>
                <p>西安地图出版社成立于1985年，是国务院新闻出版部署批准成立，国务院测绘地理信息行政主管部门核准的专业出版机构。 </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            @foreach (NewsEntityThumbUp entity in Model.NewsEntityThumbUp) {
                <div class="col-md-3 item-block animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                    <div class="fh5co-property">
                        <div class="fh5co-property-title">
                            <h5><a href="/Detail/@entity.NewsId">@entity.FullHead</a></h5>
                            <p>@Convert.ToDateTime(entity.CreateDate).ToString("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm")</p>
                        </div>
                        <figure>
                            <img src="@entity.NewsImage" alt="" class="img-responsive">
                        </figure>
                        <div class="fh5co-property-innter">
                            <p>@entity.NewsContent</p>
                        </div>
                        <p class="fh5co-property-specification">
                            <span>@entity.AuthorName</span>  <span class="comments-bar"><i class="icon-thumbs-o-up"></i>@entity.ThumbUp<i class="icon-comments"></i>@entity.CommentsCount</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>


                </div>
            }
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="fh5co-agents">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center fh5co-heading white animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                <h2>地图文化展示</h2>
                <p>为配合“美丽陕西”建设，策划出版了“地图上的秦岭系列丛书”之《秦岭全景图记》《秦岭森林公园》《秦岭地质公园》等分册 </p>
            </div>
            @foreach (NewsEntity entity in Model.MapNewsList) {
                <div class="col-md-4 text-center item-block animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">

                    <div class="fh5co-agent">
                        <figure>
                            <img class="img-responsive" src="@entity.NewsImage" alt="">
                        </figure>
                        <p>@entity.NewsContent</p>
                        <p>
                            <a href="/Detail/@entity.NewsId" class="btn btn-primary btn-outline">点击详情</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            }
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="fh5co-agents" style="background: #F6F6F6">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center fh5co-heading white animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                <h2>精品图书（推荐）</h2>
                <p>图书是人类用来记录一切成就的主要工具，也是人类交融感情，取得知识，传承经验的重要媒介。对人类文明的开展，贡献至钜。</p>
            </div>
            @foreach (NewsEntity entity in Model.PBooksList) {
                <div class="col-md-4 item-block animate-box fadeIn animated-fast" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                    <div class="fh5co-property books">
                        <figure>
                            <img src="@entity.NewsImage" alt="" class="img-responsive">
                            <a href="javascript:;" class="tag">推荐</a>
                        </figure>
                        <div class="fh5co-property-innter books">
                            <h3>
                                <a href="@entity.BuyLink">@entity.FullHead</a>
                            </h3>
                            <div class="price-status">
                                <span class="price">￥@entity.Price </span>
                            </div>
                            <p>@entity.NewsContent</p>
                        </div>
                        <p class="fh5co-property-specification books">
                            <span><strong>阅读数</strong>@entity.PV</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            }
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="fh5co-cta">
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center animate-box fadeInUp animated-fast">
            <h3>地图搜索</h3>
            <p>
                权威的地图搜索功能。权威的地图搜索功能。权威的地图搜索功能。权威的地图搜索功能。
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
<div style="background: #F6F6F6;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row"><div id="allmap" class="animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn"></div></div>
    </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    // 百度地图API功能
    var map = new BMap.Map("allmap");    // 创建Map实例
    map.centerAndZoom(new BMap.Point(116.404, 39.915), 11);  // 初始化地图,设置中心点坐标和地图级别
    map.addControl(new BMap.MapTypeControl());   //添加地图类型控件
    map.setCurrentCity("西安");          // 设置地图显示的城市 此项是必须设置的
    map.enableScrollWheelZoom(true);     //开启鼠标滚轮缩放
    var local = new BMap.LocalSearch(map, {
        renderOptions: { map: map }
    });
    local.search("西安地图出版社");

</script>

